### Pseudo code

Create a deck<br>
Shuffle deck<br>
Game starts and player draws first card

WHILE player doesn't stop the game and a value of players cards is 21 or less<br>
    player draws 1 card<br>
ENDWHILE

IF player decides to stop<br>
    dealer draws 1 card

WHILE dealer doesn't stop the game and a value of dealers cards is less then 17<br>
    dealer draws 1 card<br>
ENDWHILE

IF dealer has 21 or is closer to 21 or dealers score is the same as players score<br>
    dealer wins<br>
ELSE<br>
    player wins